precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a TREATY ON
MUTUAL ASSISTANCE IN CRIMINAL MATTERS between Canada and the KINGDOM OF
BELGIUM, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing either
the Hon. Allan Rock or Ambassador Jean-Paul Hubert to sign the said Treaty.
